commit.message:
S/390: Remove internal builtins from vecintrin.h.

gcc/ChangeLog:

2015-06-24  Andreas Krebbel  <krebbel@linux.vnet.ibm.com>

	    * config/s390/vecintrin.h: Remove internal builtins.

From-SVN: r224871
